						<div class="credit"><div class="author contributor">
<div class="avatar-container">
 <a href="https://globalvoices.org/author/oiwan/"><a href='https://globalvoices.org/author/oiwan/' class='url user-link' title='View all posts by Oiwan Lam'><img src='https://globalvoices.org/wp-content/uploads/local-avatars/254.jpg' alt='' class='avatar photo author-profile-pic'  style='height:64px;width:64px;' /></a></a></div><!--.avatar-container-->
<div class="contributor-name"><span class="credit-label">Written by</span><a href="https://globalvoices.org/author/oiwan/" class="url user-link" title="Oiwan Lam">Oiwan Lam</a></div><!--.contributor-name--></div>
 <!--.contributor-->
